text: Timur Talgatovich Dosmagambetov (, ; born 1 May 1989) is a Kazakhstani footballer who plays as a midfielder for Ordabasy and the Kazakhstan national team. ==Career== Dosmagambetov made his international debut for Kazakhstan on 12 May 2015 in a friendly match against Burkina Faso, which finished as a 0–0 draw. ==Career statistics== ===International=== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:center" |- !colspan=3|Kazakhstan |- !Year!!Apps!!Goals |- |2015||3||0 |- |2016||2||0 |- !Total!!5!!0 |} ==References== ==External links== * * * * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:People from Kokshetau Category:Kazakhstani footballers Category:Kazakhstan under-21 international footballers Category:Kazakhstan international footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC Okzhetpes players Category:FC Aktobe players Category:FC Vostok players Category:FC Taraz players Category:FC Tobol players Category:FC Ordabasy players Category:Kazakhstan Premier League players
